values: haven't put anything on here for a while bcuz i've been extremely busy workin and shit. but now i don't have a job anymore so i'm starting to get extremely bor'd again. i hung out with the girls last week and got fucked up at a party we all endedup pretty proper. but hey i just thought i'd put somthing up. i'm doin alrite don't feel like i'm dying so i guess that alrite

i've decided taht i'm goin to quit sleeping now. i only slept like a half hour last nite and i'm running fine today so i figured i can go without sleep for a while. really i just want to get some sleep depravation goin on so i can trip out for a while. rite now i'm up at cassie's house just watchin pulp fiction. i had a lot of fun lastnite we just stayed up here it was me cassie felicia and black. we just drank a lil bit and got feeling proper. well i'm off so i can get around and take a shower and shit so i'm clean haha.

i just woke up about an hour ago. i spent the night with cassie, i love this gurl so much it's crzy. we just watched movies last nite and hung out with some friends for a little while. The big party starts today whenever we feel like actually going to it. I broke down yesterday and we had to puch the car up summer hill so then we could coast down the other side haha it was fukin great. then when the car got close to cassie's house i had to jump out cuz if we stopped the car wouldn't start bak up again, but i love my gurl so much that jumping out the car really didn't bother me. i just can't get over how much i love this gurl already it's really crzy.

Today we woke up extremely early i have idea why except for the fuking fact that it feels like my whole body is having trembles. Last nite we just chilled out and drank, surprisingly i drank enuff to kill a small elephant but still wasn't drunk it was kinda dissapointing in the long run. but really taht's all i have to say rite now cuz i need to go do somthing.
